Attention

Sequel to the meeting held in Washington DC with American Senators and
in line with the Executive Order signed by the newly Inaugurated
President of America, President Joe Biden, on 17th of March 2021. Be
informed that he has instructed that all outstanding foreign debt
accruing from INHERITANCE FUNDS, WINNING FUNDS TRAPPED IN LOCAL AND
FOREIGN BANKS, SCAM VICTIMS, and its associated cases should be
compensated immediately with the sum of $250,000.00 without further
delay through this office We discovered that you were misled by some
officials and Individuals, who took advantage of you, as a result,
demanded one payment after another from you without releasing your
funds to you. You are to get back to us with your current address
and telephone numbers for further Clarifications as may be required so
that your transaction will be processed and concluded immediately.

You are warned to stop further communication with anybody concerning
your payment with effect from today to enable you to receive your fund
successfully without further delay. Your payment file is right here
with us and we are set to complete your payment immediately as
instructed by President Joe Biden, and the ministry of internal
affairs.

Further advice shall be given to you as soon as we hear from you.

YOURS FAITHFULLY
Pierre Guénant
For:
US Board Compensation Committee.
